01:40:40.728 --> 01:40:41.504
Come on!

01:40:41.528 --> 01:40:42.528
Let's go!

01:40:42.553 --> 01:40:45.406
(But Su Yeon from the Marine Corps is
turning the game around immediately.)

01:40:45.486 --> 01:40:47.608
But Su Yeon is getting back up.

01:40:47.608 --> 01:40:48.772
- Wait!
- This is...

01:40:48.908 --> 01:40:49.908
(Don't even think about it.)

01:40:49.933 --> 01:40:50.973
She's pulling her back!

01:40:52.540 --> 01:40:54.745
The physique difference is quite big!

01:40:54.788 --> 01:40:57.198
(Su Yeon's physique is leaving
everyone in awe.)

01:40:57.198 --> 01:40:58.198
She's so strong.

01:41:00.301 --> 01:41:02.107
She put my face in the water,

01:41:02.131 --> 01:41:03.687
which made me really angry.

01:41:04.037 --> 01:41:05.956
So, I planned on planting her down
by the trench wall.

01:41:06.367 --> 01:41:07.558
Plant her down by the trench wall!

01:41:07.583 --> 01:41:09.760
- No, you have to get her out!
- Focus on getting her out!

01:41:09.760 --> 01:41:11.128
Su Yeon is mad now!

01:41:11.518 --> 01:41:13.288
(Su Yeon, of the Marine Corps,
is enraged.)

01:41:13.312 --> 01:41:14.653
Come on!

01:41:14.677 --> 01:41:15.789
- Keep going!
- Su Yeon!

01:41:15.983 --> 01:41:17.591
She's dragging her out!

01:41:17.616 --> 01:41:18.784
- Hold up!
- She's stopping her.

01:41:18.859 --> 01:41:20.594
- She's mad.
- She's enraged!

01:41:20.594 --> 01:41:21.802
(Hyeon Seon has no way to get out.)

01:41:21.802 --> 01:41:22.802
Hyeon Seon!

01:41:23.257 --> 01:41:24.638
She's unbelievably strong.

01:41:25.305 --> 01:41:26.413
Her strength is insane.

01:41:26.961 --> 01:41:28.312
- You have to stay strong!
- Stay strong!

01:41:28.312 --> 01:41:30.681
Su Yeon is absolutely fuming now.

01:41:30.681 --> 01:41:32.516
Hyeon Seon is facing her biggest threat.

01:41:32.516 --> 01:41:35.385
I couldn't get a grip on myself,
but I tried to last as long as possible.

01:41:35.669 --> 01:41:37.387
- Hyeon Seon, stay in there!
- Stay strong!

01:41:37.412 --> 01:41:38.458
She's no match against her
when it's 1-on-1.

01:41:38.458 --> 01:41:39.856
- She doesn't stand a chance!
- Out!

01:41:41.302 --> 01:41:42.409
- Hyeon Seon...
- Who's out?

01:41:42.409 --> 01:41:43.727
- A Ra and Bo Ram?
- They're out?

01:41:43.727 --> 01:41:44.995
Not Hyeon Seon?

01:41:45.592 --> 01:41:47.064
(Is it Cho A Ra of the Marine Corps?)

01:41:47.224 --> 01:41:48.532
Who is it?

01:41:48.557 --> 01:41:50.734
- It's not Hyeon Seon?
- This won't do.

01:41:51.285 --> 01:41:51.754
Come on!

01:41:51.778 --> 01:41:53.570
Did Bo Ram get A Ra out?

01:41:53.595 --> 01:41:54.561
This will turn the whole game around!

01:41:54.561 --> 01:41:55.752
It's the other two?

01:41:56.645 --> 01:41:57.705
What's going on?

01:41:58.041 --> 01:41:59.309
Bo Ram and A Ra!

01:41:59.334 --> 01:42:00.510
Stay strong!

01:42:00.510 --> 01:42:02.033
You have to stay in there!

01:42:02.121 --> 01:42:03.121
It must be A Ra!

01:42:03.146 --> 01:42:04.348
This won't do!

01:42:04.411 --> 01:42:07.184
Sit down!

01:42:07.184 --> 01:42:09.249
- You have to stay in there!
- Bo Ram lifted...

01:42:10.150 --> 01:42:11.588
A Ra!

01:42:11.735 --> 01:42:12.789
It's game over.

01:42:12.789 --> 01:42:13.724
She can't last against two people.

01:42:13.724 --> 01:42:14.992
That makes it 2-on-1 now.

01:42:16.426 --> 01:42:17.771
(Bo Ram flipped A Ra over in a blink.)

01:42:17.771 --> 01:42:18.771
Cho A Ra is out!

01:42:18.806 --> 01:42:20.631
The 707th Group stands a better chance
at winning now!

01:42:21.064 --> 01:42:22.532
The 707th Group is insane.

01:42:22.833 --> 01:42:24.368
Right on! Keep going!

01:42:24.368 --> 01:42:25.554
- Take her out right away!
- Hurry!

01:42:25.579 --> 01:42:26.570
Come on!

01:42:27.161 --> 01:42:29.984
(Just as A Ra got out...)

01:42:31.999 --> 01:42:33.477
- Hyeon Seon!
- It's 1-on-1 now!

01:42:33.502 --> 01:42:34.581
- She got out at the same time as A Ra!
- This is so...

01:42:34.581 --> 01:42:35.412
Hyeon Seon...

01:42:35.412 --> 01:42:36.680
I saw her fly!

01:42:38.385 --> 01:42:41.318
How strong is she?

01:42:41.477 --> 01:42:42.477
That's insane.

01:42:43.243 --> 01:42:44.243
No way.

01:42:44.717 --> 01:42:46.286
(Even the Tarantula Unit soldier
is in awe.)

01:42:46.553 --> 01:42:47.724
It's 1-on-1 now.

01:42:47.749 --> 01:42:49.749
Bo Ram of the 707th Group
and Su Yeon of the Marine Corps!

01:42:49.893 --> 01:42:51.665
Bo Ram is pushing Su Yeon from behind!

01:42:51.665 --> 01:42:52.929
Push her right now!

01:42:52.929 --> 01:42:53.929
- Right now!
- Keep going!

01:42:54.464 --> 01:42:56.358
- Keep going until the end!
- You still have one more.

01:42:56.382 --> 01:42:57.601
Su Yeon is turning around!

01:42:57.771 --> 01:42:58.771
Su Yeon is turning around now!

01:42:59.074 --> 01:43:00.074
My gosh!

01:43:00.307 --> 01:43:01.938
- Move faster!
- Come on!

01:43:02.021 --> 01:43:03.607
- The other way!
- Turn around!

01:43:03.632 --> 01:43:04.229
Go under!

01:43:04.253 --> 01:43:05.542
Su Yeon is grabbing Bo Ram's pants.

01:43:05.542 --> 01:43:06.677
Bo Ram is still going strong!

01:43:06.747 --> 01:43:08.612
- Come on!
- Grab her legs!

01:43:09.456 --> 01:43:10.597
(Su Yeon from the Marine Corps is
striking back.)

01:43:10.622 --> 01:43:11.231
She did it!

01:43:11.256 --> 01:43:12.486
- No!
- Come on!

01:43:12.486 --> 01:43:13.687
- Don't lift her!
- Bo Ram!

01:43:14.521 --> 01:43:16.119
(She stayed strong!)

01:43:16.830 --> 01:43:18.792
(Bo Ram's other leg barely managed
to stay on the ground.)

01:43:18.921 --> 01:43:20.503
Bo Ram is going strong.

01:43:21.488 --> 01:43:22.723
(Bo Ram is hugging Su Yeon's leg.)

01:43:22.723 --> 01:43:24.161
- She has to stay strong here.
- This is...

01:43:25.028 --> 01:43:27.130
I stuck to Su Yeon,

01:43:27.698 --> 01:43:29.332
but it felt like an elephant was
stepping on me.

01:43:29.332 --> 01:43:31.168
- She's called a boar and an elephant!
- I couldn't let her...

01:43:31.168 --> 01:43:33.570
beat me here,

01:43:33.570 --> 01:43:35.105
so I kept going for her.

01:43:35.539 --> 01:43:37.407
She's so determined!

01:43:37.432 --> 01:43:38.211
Seriously.

01:43:38.211 --> 01:43:39.543
She's so stubborn.

01:43:41.211 --> 01:43:45.315
Sergeant Park kept her legs crossed.

01:43:45.916 --> 01:43:48.552
She was basically an anaconda.

01:43:49.753 --> 01:43:51.254
No, take your leg out right now!

01:43:51.792 --> 01:43:53.123
Come on! Take your leg out!

01:43:53.123 --> 01:43:54.191
Grab her leg!

01:43:54.216 --> 01:43:55.899
- You have to grab her leg!
- Grab it!

01:43:55.899 --> 01:43:57.337
(Su Yeon keeps attacking Bo Ram,
but Bo Ram is persistent.)

01:43:57.337 --> 01:43:58.337
Yes, keep going!

01:43:59.466 --> 01:44:00.897
- Push her out!
- Come on!

01:44:00.897 --> 01:44:02.766
- One more time!
- Just on your left!

01:44:02.970 --> 01:44:05.338
- Right on!
- Just a little more!

01:44:05.891 --> 01:44:07.020
Get your leg out and go again.

01:44:07.521 --> 01:44:08.622
- No!
- What?

01:44:09.036 --> 01:44:10.998
(Bo Ram is even looking
for a chance to strike back.)

01:44:10.998 --> 01:44:12.275
I can't tell who's going to win.

01:44:12.300 --> 01:44:13.376
Let's go!

01:44:15.184 --> 01:44:16.613
This 1-on-1 battle...

01:44:16.823 --> 01:44:18.348
Su Yeon's leg is tied down.

01:44:18.615 --> 01:44:21.451
This means that Su Yeon can't use
her full strength either.

01:44:21.575 --> 01:44:22.185
Bo Ram!

01:44:22.185 --> 01:44:23.697
Bo Ram is much smaller, but...

01:44:23.697 --> 01:44:25.425
- Come on, Bo Ram!
- Bo Ram is so...

01:44:25.450 --> 01:44:26.456
You're doing great!

01:44:26.456 --> 01:44:27.941
Bo Ram is still going strong.

01:44:29.169 --> 01:44:30.311
(The big tree has fallen.)

01:44:30.311 --> 01:44:32.172
- That was so sudden!
- She tripped her over!

01:44:32.172 --> 01:44:33.897
- What?
- She's striking back!

01:44:33.897 --> 01:44:34.897
(This can't be.)

01:44:36.125 --> 01:44:37.434
Bo Ram is striking back!

01:44:37.731 --> 01:44:39.402
Su Yeon is now down!

01:44:39.402 --> 01:44:40.771
You got this!

01:44:40.771 --> 01:44:41.571
You did it!

01:44:41.571 --> 01:44:42.873
- Bo Ram is striking back!
- Right on!

01:44:42.898 --> 01:44:43.911
You got this!

01:44:44.224 --> 01:44:45.224
No way.

01:44:45.539 --> 01:44:46.810
I'm getting goosebumps.

01:44:52.119 --> 01:44:55.188
(Su Yeon is thrown off
by the unexpected attack.)

01:44:55.363 --> 01:44:58.555
If Su Yeon loses now...

01:44:58.555 --> 01:45:00.357
I have no idea who's going to win.

01:45:00.574 --> 01:45:02.425
